Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Demon Beast Invasion 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet another\Nunsuitable woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?!\N- I've found you, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi Kasu. So, the failed\Nteacher has become an agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the Interplanetary Mutual\NObservation Treaty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I sentence you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try it... if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto... What the\Nhell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasu...\NWhat happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU happened to my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there,\Nafter him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who's supposed to\Ndrive me after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called you and called you!\NWhat the hell were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was sorta\Noccupied with a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were WHAT?!\NI'm out here risking my ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while you're dipping\Nyour wick with some wornan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she wasn't\Njust "some woman!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wasn't doing this I'd\Nbe a lot happier, believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You expect to defend the peace\Nof Earth like that, you dipshit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out! Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasu! Kasul
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will never capture me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shomei Prefectural College
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Music Department
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day,\Nright Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Tsutomu.\NSomebody's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one'll be coming at\Nthis time of the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that time\Nof the month for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?! I've never heard of\N"that time of the month"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...being 30 days long!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand!\NI can't wait any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give a guy an\Nirresponsible boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you get a helper\Nwith lots of problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto... He knows\Nwhat I look like, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to look\Nfor him by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take 'im out...\NGot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right... It's Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, this is really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been four... No,\NFIVE years since you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is something.\NYou and Kayo at the same school!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess God wanted\Nus together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo loves you, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you love her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell her how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and tell her. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I can still\Nlove her when we're apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu, I want you to\Ntake care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You love her too,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That promise is still\Nin effect, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear\Nabout you wanting het back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, she's even\Nmore beautiful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bet you're jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoulda had more foresight.\NDamn right I'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back in one piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi Kasu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dipshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutting out in the middle\Nof a case to go partying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I've got\Na life of my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes don't have lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We defend the\Npeace of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Day and night, that's all\Nwe should ever live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what real\Nheroes are made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiny little apartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instant ramen meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No sex to speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real heroes never\Ncomplain about any of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real heroism\Nequals real poverty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have\Nto remember this:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate scallion and\Nfermented bean curd!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My nose is more sensitive\Nthan most people's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So strong-smelling\Nfood is right out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run through\Nthis one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two reasons why the Demon\NBeasts are taking over human bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first is because they\Njust can't take Earth's atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second is the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to cross-breed\Nwith humans to adapt to the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so that they can\Nconquer the planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GOT THAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we gotta be suspicious\Nof anyone who's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...suddenly started\Nhitting on women big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta check 'em out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand, Muneto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heroes who fight\Nfor the peace of all space!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So get with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a hero sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how serious\NTsutomu was before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I do it with anyone,\Nit'll have to be Tsutomu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lady-killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just if you might\Nknow anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody who just suddenly\Nstarted really chasing women.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. There's a guy named\NMaeda in my class like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like something's\Ncome over him lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's tried to pick up\Nlots of women already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a class photo from\Nthe beginning of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where did I put it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... Hmmm...\NHold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love Tsutomu,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you. It's really\Ngreat to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- See you later, then.\N- Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That son of a...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's Maeda...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.44,0:22:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Tsutomu?\N- Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem,\NTsutomu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!\NHow could you, Muneto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know where\Nyou were last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Kayo! I'm not just\Ngoing to let you take her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.\NI'm not trying to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.92,0:22:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just talking\Nabout old times last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.59,0:22:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.59,0:22:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always did\Njump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to say I wouldn't\Nlike another shot at her...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, I can control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.19,0:22:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police!\NCall the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:22:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.57,0:23:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse rne. What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I blew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dipshit! You had\Nhim and let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.91,0:23:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're gonna pay a call\Non Mr. Maeda tonight. Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.85,0:24:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of Kayo Asakura's\Nfriends, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.14,0:24:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.57,0:24:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru Maeda
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.21,0:24:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.05,0:24:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kasu!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.22,0:24:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.64,0:24:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.85,0:24:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.94,0:24:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.06,0:24:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you\Ndoing here so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.23,0:25:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought I'd take\Nyou for a drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.82,0:25:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasu! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.21,0:25:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.21,0:25:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.48,0:25:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.33,0:25:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're too late!\NKayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.75,0:25:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.00,0:26:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I had an\Noutstanding nose, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.26,0:26:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got good\Ntaste in perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.30,0:26:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be able\Nto find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.85,0:26:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.48,0:26:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Tokyo looks\Nbest from here at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.65,0:26:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.99,0:26:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo... I really want\Nthis to be the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.45,0:26:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.96,0:26:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we were kids,\NI've only had eyes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.08,0:26:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.54,0:26:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.03,0:27:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.58,0:27:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.00,0:28:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.13,0:28:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.72,0:29:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time...\NThis time I go all the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.00,0:29:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.69,0:29:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KAYO!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.99,0:29:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.03,0:29:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sorry couple of agents!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.33,0:30:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.00,0:30:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.38,0:30:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.27,0:30:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.02,0:30:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.28,0:30:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.07,0:30:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.70,0:30:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tsutomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.07,0:30:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.38,0:30:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.61,0:31:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me.\NWhat's happened to Tsutomu?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.00,0:31:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.00,0:31:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's an alien\Nfrom quasar PHL-5200.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.31,0:31:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We call them Demon Beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.98,0:31:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Beasts...?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.32,0:32:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their ultimate goal is the\Nconquest of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.91,0:32:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the atmosphere now isn't\Nsuitable to support them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.67,0:32:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they have to take\Nover peoples' bodies. Use them...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.14,0:32:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.35,0:32:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto and I\Nare agents of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.19,0:32:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Interplanetary Mutual\NObservation Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.61,0:32:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was created to oppose any\Nillegal planetary incursions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.86,0:32:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the Earth still\Ndon't know we even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.99,0:32:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I couldn't\Ntell you, Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.00,0:32:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.63,0:32:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Tsutomu?\NCan you save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.47,0:33:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Once a Demon\NBeast takes someone over...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.04,0:33:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu... I really thought\NI could let you have Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.28,0:34:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, of all times...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.24,0:34:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.96,0:34:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing... disguised\Nas Tsutomu... was so...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.64,0:34:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.98,0:34:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.94,0:34:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.24,0:34:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.91,0:34:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.99,0:34:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.59,0:35:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo's on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.18,0:35:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I expected, the Demon\NBeast'e still after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.31,0:35:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop her, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.85,0:35:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way we'll ever\Ntrack this thing down...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.10,0:35:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is to use her as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.85,0:35:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you do\Nthat to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.81,0:35:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Link up with me ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.77,0:35:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasu...!\NThat scheming old...!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.59,0:35:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.84,0:35:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.55,0:35:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.77,0:36:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you\Na taste of paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.38,0:36:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.84,0:36:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.34,0:36:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you to that to them...\NTo Kayo... To my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.56,0:36:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.52,0:36:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when things\Nwere getting good!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.11,0:36:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That toy can't hurt me!\NIt barely tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.20,0:37:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damned invader!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.75,0:37:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Invader? Hardly!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.54,0:37:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred million years ago,\Nour ancestors left this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.55,0:37:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when an accident changed\Nthe planet's environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.43,0:37:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were the first\Ninhabitants of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.97,0:37:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.61,0:37:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.81,0:37:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happened in the past,\Nthe Earth belongs to humans now!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.57,0:37:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're invaders,\Nno matter what they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.90,0:37:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Beasts who stole\Nyour friend's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.78,0:37:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, the guns are useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.91,0:37:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.04,0:37:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you use my friend!\NUse Tsutomu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.89,0:38:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.14,0:38:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.15,0:38:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.16,0:38:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now to put you\Nout of my misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.17,0:38:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.22,0:38:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still Tsutomu!\NTry to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.93,0:38:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.89,0:38:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.23,0:38:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.57,0:38:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.57,0:39:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka... yo...!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.53,0:39:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.91,0:39:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.71,0:39:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.47,0:39:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KASU!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.14,0:39:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, forget me!\NSHOOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.54,0:39:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto... I'm sorry\NI used Kayo as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.22,0:40:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.27,0:40:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto... Finish him\Noff with your Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.86,0:40:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.19,0:40:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.53,0:40:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.53,0:40:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.18,0:40:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu... Kasu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.79,0:41:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.83,0:41:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.38,0:41:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...\NTake care of Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.78,0:41:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Kasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.16,0:41:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.45,0:42:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.87,0:42:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up! You're a hero,\Nwho saved the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.17,0:42:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.17,0:42:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're down all the time,\Nyou'll never get anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.84,0:42:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.51,0:42:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women have to be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.85,0:42:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't,\Nyou can't live...
